upload2Kindle
=============

WARNING:
--------
upload2Kindle uses tls to email the file using gmail which is insecure.  Also your gmail password is stored in plain text.

Blurb:
------
Easily upload files to your Amazon Kindle via Whispernet using your Send-to-Kindle e-mail address.

Description:
------------
upload2Kindle uses the sendEmail command line SMTP email client to email a personal document or book to a Send-to-Kindle email address <'user'@free.kindle.com>

Requirements:
-------------
 - sendEmail version 1.56-2

